summary:
Motivated second year International Business student working towards the Bachelor of Business Administration in Utrecht. I strive to become the best version of myself by working hard and learning from highs and lows every day. 

I am passionate about traveling which is one of the reasons why I enjoy my studies as I learn about different cultures and how it translates to the working environment. I am a team player, organized and have a positive attitude. Ready to develop new skills and gain knowledge to be successful!
